text: Chekhrak () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Dmitriyevskoye Rural Settlement of Koshekhablsky District, Adygea, Russia. The population was 506 as of 2018. There are 10 streets. == References == Category:Rural localities in Koshekhablsky District
title: Chekhrak, Dmitriyevskoye Rural Settlement, Koshekhablsky District, Republic of Adygea
